data.description: Motivated Seller !!!! Isn't she lovely! A Spacious home built in 2019 with 5 bedrooms 3 full baths...  located in Southwest Allen County school district, has many features to offer. Over 3,000 sq ft with an open floor plan that is great for entertaining. The kitchen has many upgrades which includes Granite countertops, walk in pantry that provides extra space, nice center island All appliances stay!! The family-room has surround sound (as well as other parts of the home) and is open to the kitchen which allows easy entertaining. The extra living space on the main level can be play-room area or can be a multi-purpose room, dining room, formal living or an office. The 5th bedroom located on main floor would also make a great guest room or office. This home does not lack the space, the loft is another multi-purpose area. The Grand Owners suite has massive walk-in closets with a double sink, soaking tub and shower. Motivated seller offering $5,000 buyer credit towards down payment.
